<p><strong>Description</strong></p>
<p>SlenderMod is a project created by Tim Spaninks and Marco van den Oever which originally started as a simple modification of the original slenderman game by Parsec. Instead of simply building a new level for the game we ended up creating a complete remake of the game. </p>
<p>We don't have the intention to 'steal' anything made by Parsec. We really enjoyed his game and thought it was a great concept. We did this project mostly for our own enjoyment, learning purposes and hopefully to scare the crap out of as many people as possible. Enjoy!</p>
