<p><strong>Controls</strong></p>
<p>Movement:      WASD<br />Orientation:     Mouse<br />Pickup Notes:   Left Mouse Button<br />Sprint:              Shift</p>
<p><strong>Story</strong></p>
<div style="float: clear;">Slender Man (a.k.a Slenderman) is a mythical creature often depicted as a tall, thin figure wearing a black suit and a blank face. According to the legend, he can stretch or shorten his arms at will and has tentacle-like appendages protruding from his back. Depending on the interpretations of the myth, the creature can cause memory loss, insomnia, paranoia, coughing fits (nicknamed “slendersickness”), photograph/video distortions and can teleport at will. The urban legend has inspired fan arts, fictional <a href="http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/creepypasta">creepypastas</a> and a mockumentary series in the style of the 1999 indie horror film <em>Blair Witch Project</em>. <a href="http://knowyourmeme.com/memes/slender-man">[know your meme]</a></div>
